Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.67,Latin,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:06.43,Latin,,0,0,0,,welcome to soteriology.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:10.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,This course deals with the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:14.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,and the doctrine of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:16.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,how the Holy Spirit works in the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:20.37,Latin,,0,0,0,,Running all the way from His effectual calling,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,and regeneration,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,all the way to glorification.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:29.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,So it's a very important subject
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:33.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,and I'm glad you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:37.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,We're going to look at it in some detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:41.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,I think you'll enjoy the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:45.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,all of our
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,Christianity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,all of our personal religion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:53.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,is just a sham without the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:55.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,So we're very,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,very grateful for the ministry of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,I want to begin this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:06.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,first lecture with the reading of God's word,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:10.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,as we will with each each lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:12.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,Turn with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:13.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,please,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:17.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,to Romans 8 and I'll read 13 through 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:21.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,Romans 8: 13 through 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,For,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:26.92,Latin,,0,0,0,,if you live after the flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:29.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,you shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,But if ye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:33.27,Latin,,0,0,0,,through the Spirit do mortify,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:35.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,the deeds of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:38.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,ye shall live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.94,Latin,,0,0,0,,For as many as are led
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:43.76,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the Spirit of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:46.76,Latin,,0,0,0,,they are the sons of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,For you have not received the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,of bondage again to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,but you have received the Spirit of adoption
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,whereby we cry Abba,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:02.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Spirit itself beareth witness with our spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we are the children of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:12.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,and if children then heirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,heirs of God and joint heirs with Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,If so be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.48,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we suffer with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:25.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we may also be glorified together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:29.92,Latin,,0,0,0,,Let's seek God's face in prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,Lord God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:35.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,we stand on holy ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,as we approach this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:43.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,immense subject of the third person of the Holy Trinity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:48.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,and his salvific work in our souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.79,Latin,,0,0,0,,And we do pray that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the end of this course,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:57.32,Latin,,0,0,0,,we will have a much more profound appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:01.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,for the saving ministry of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:05.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,than we perhaps might have at present
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help us to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:12.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,not only in the grace and knowledge of Jesus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:15.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,whom the Spirit focuses upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,but also that we would grow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the grace and knowledge of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:26.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,becoming more aware of His work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.53,Latin,,0,0,0,,His saving work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,and appreciating more profoundly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:34.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,the vastness of His ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.42,Latin,,0,0,0,,as he works in sinners and rebels,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:42.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,such as we all are by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:46.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,So Lord bless this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:48.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help me in teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help the students in listening,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,learning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,and grant that each lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:59.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,may serve to thy glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,to our spiritual growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to the well-being
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:08.32,Latin,,0,0,0,,of our entire being as we journey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:12.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,to the never-ending eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,Be with us now we pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,In Jesus name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,thank you for joining us for this class
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.99,Latin,,0,0,0,,and I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,begin with the first lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is titled: The Study
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:39.43,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Study of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:45.43,Latin,,0,0,0,,God's Holy spirit was with God's people from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:49.02,Latin,,0,0,0,,Already in Genesis 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.98,Latin,,0,0,0,,verse 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:55.88,Latin,,0,0,0,,leading them ultimately to their rest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:05:02.33,Latin,,0,0,0,,in Jesus Christ (Isaiah 63 14)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,To know the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:10.16,Latin,,0,0,0,,therefore is to stand in continuity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,with the Saints of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,God has promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,his Spirit already to Israel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.79,Latin,,0,0,0,,His chosen people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,We know that in the Old Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.33,Latin,,0,0,0,,various individuals experience a comfort of that Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,Think of David,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:35.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,for example (Psalm 51)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,But God promised
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.88,Latin,,0,0,0,,a far richer and broader work of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:46.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,than we might possibly imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.94,Latin,,0,0,0,,Isaiah foretold of a righteous king
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:53.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,whose administration would be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:56.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,rivers of waters in a dry place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,and the transformation of the barren wilderness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:05.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,into a world filled with the fruit of righteousness (Isaiah 32).
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:08.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,When the Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.48,Latin,,0,0,0,,When the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.53,Latin,,0,0,0,,is poured out upon us from on high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:18.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,And then he goes on to say in Isaiah 44,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:22.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,that the Spirit would be poured out on Israel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:23.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,like a river
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:26.53,Latin,,0,0,0,,of water on dry ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,irrigating faithless souls to produce a people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:35.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,who say I am the Lord's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the answer of God's covenantal faithfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.71,Latin,,0,0,0,,to the chronic problem
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:48.03,Latin,,0,0,0,,of Israel's covenant breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,You find that also in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,the Book of Joel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,that the Lord would pour out his Spirit upon all his people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.11,Latin,,0,0,0,,that whosoever would call on the name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Lord would be saved
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:07.91,Latin,,0,0,0,,(Joel 2:28 to 32).
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:11.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,So to study the work of the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.37,Latin,,0,0,0,,is to study heavenly work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,And work that abides forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.71,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the New Testament age you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,that when Jesus rose from the dead
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,and ascended into heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,He poured out His Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,in much larger measures than
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,had previously been known
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:48.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,(Acts 2 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:53.23,Latin,,0,0,0,,through 21 and 33 and 34)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,And Peter after his sermon is interrupted by
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:02.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,thousands of people who are under great conviction of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.53,Latin,,0,0,0,,Under it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,and they cried out men and Brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,Peter said to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.76,Latin,,0,0,0,,repent and be baptized everyone of you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the name of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.88,Latin,,0,0,0,,And you shall receive the gift of the Holy Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,For the promise is unto you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to your children
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.97,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to all that are afar off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.92,Latin,,0,0,0,,Even as many as the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:39.92,Latin,,0,0,0,,Our God shall call (Acts 2: 38 and 39).
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:46.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the New Testament writings,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,particularly Paul's Epistles,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:53.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,are just filled with the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,He speaks often
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,about being born
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit such as Galatians,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,4: 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.76,Latin,,0,0,0,,And he's talking constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,about different aspects
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit's saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,Like we just read a few
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,of them to you from from Romans 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:22.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,So if we treasure Christ as our only mediator,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,we will also treasure the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:29.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,as Christ's great gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is inseparable from Him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:35.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,to sinners (John 4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:38.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,and again John 7).
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:43.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,Jonathan Edwards put it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,"The sum of the blessings Christ sought
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,by what he did and suffered
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.27,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the work of redemption,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:55.27,Latin,,0,0,0,,was the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.42,Latin,,0,0,0,,the Holy Spirit in His indwelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:01.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,His influences and fruits
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:04.23,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the sum of all grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,holiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,comfort and joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,or in one word
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:14.16,Latin,,0,0,0,,of all the spiritual good Christ purchased
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:16.59,Latin,,0,0,0,,for men in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:20.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,And is also the sum of all perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,and eternal joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,that he purchased
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:29.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,for them in another world."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,That's an amazing quote by Edwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,And it certainly shows us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:40.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,that many today are minimizing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,the role of the ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.71,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Holy Spirit as
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,integral with the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.77,Latin,,0,0,0,,sum of blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:55.02,Latin,,0,0,0,,that God's people receive in salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:58.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,John Brown of Headington
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,put it this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:04.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,"Did Christ purchase the Holy Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,Christ purchased the Spirit's gifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:11.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,and influences in applying redemption,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,but not his being,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is independent."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,So the work of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.68,Latin,,0,0,0,,in many ways
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,of Christ's death and resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.91,Latin,,0,0,0,,salvation in Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,is appreciated and enjoyed therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,only by knowing the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,and his saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.37,Latin,,0,0,0,,And this is one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.57,Latin,,0,0,0,,greatest doctrines of the Reformation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.42,Latin,,0,0,0,,developed so thoroughly and then even
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:54.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,augmented by the Puritans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:12:00.04,Latin,,0,0,0,,What a treasure Reformed theology brings us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:04.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,about the saving ministry of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:10.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,BB Warfield called John Calvin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Theologian of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:15.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,And Warfield went on to claim
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,the developed doctrine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the work of the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:24.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,is an exclusively Reformation doctrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:27.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,and more particularly a Reformed doctrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:31.98,Latin,,0,0,0,,and still more particularly a Puritan doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,study of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:41.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,through Reformed experiential soteriology,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,- that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:46.59,Latin,,0,0,0,,salvation that we experience
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the work
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.42,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit in the soul -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,opens up a vast wealth of wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,and joy to the believer.
